/build
# NOTE: dist/ must NOT be ignored — the frontend static build is deployed to production via /app/frontend/dist
# dist/
# dist

# Environment files
# NOTE: .env files MUST be committed to the repo — Emergent K8s deployment
# overwrites them with production values at deploy time. Blocking them here
# breaks production deploys (deployment_agent flagged this as BLOCKER).

*token.json*
*credentials.json*

# Logs and debug files
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*
dump.rdb

# System files
.DS_Store
*.pem

# Python
